import React, { useContext } from "react"; import FortniteContext from "../context/FortniteContext"; export default function Table() { const context = useContext(FortniteContext); const { usersDataOne, usersDataTwo } = context; return (
Users : {usersDataOne?.name} {usersDataTwo?.name}
Nível nesta temporada : {usersDataOne?.account.level} {usersDataTwo?.account.level}
Soma dos níveis : {usersDataOne?.accountLevelHistory .map((obj) => obj.level).reduce((a, b) => a + b)} {usersDataTwo?.accountLevelHistory .map((obj) => obj.level).reduce((a, b) => a + b)}
Stats do solo : {usersDataOne?.accountLevelHistory .map((obj) => obj.level).reduce((a, b) => a + b)} {usersDataTwo?.accountLevelHistory .map((obj) => obj.level).reduce((a, b) => a + b)}
) }
